[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 104     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m ### Issue ARCH-4: Enrollment Photo Staleness Not Enforced in Code (LOW)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      107[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **The problem:** Lambda cold starts can add 1-3 seconds to the first invocation after a period of inactivity. For a check-in kiosk, this means the first patient of the day (or after a lull) experiences 2-5 second latency. The performance table states 0.8-2 seconds without noting this is for warm invocations.
