[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      136[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Suggested fix:** Add one sentence to the Code Step 1 or Prerequisites: "The live photo is included in the API request body (base64-encoded, under API Gateway's 10MB payload limit). For higher-resolution images, consider pre-signed S3 upload URLs with short expiration." Very minor.
